{"TopicId":145603,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Command Seat IVA","CreatedByName":"The_Rocketeer","CreatedById":81727,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T14:18:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The_Rocketeer","CreatedById":81727,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T14:18:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone know of a way to either give the EAS-1 Command Seat an IVA, or to lock the camera to a crew perspective from a command seat? This seems like such a simple thing and since I\u0027m on the point of setting out on an epic rover journey I\u0027d like to sort it out one way or the other before hand.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nSimply to avoid people suggesting it I have tried using \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Umbra Space Industries (a collection of mods)\u0022\u003EUSI\u003C/abbr\u003E Exploration\u0027s HERP seat but it seems to be broken - an issue I\u0027ve already flagging in the dev thread for that mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dafidge9898","CreatedById":147547,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T16:25:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709439\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470665922\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281727\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Rocketeer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The_Rocketeer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone know of a way to either give the EAS-1 Command Seat an IVA, or to lock the camera to a crew perspective from a command seat? This seems like such a simple thing and since I\u0027m on the point of setting out on an epic rover journey I\u0027d like to sort it out one way or the other before hand.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can\u0027t really fly from the kerbal\u0027s point of view if he\u0027s outside the spacecraft. You could press V until you get to \u0022Locked\u0022, that way your view follows whatever direction your rover happens to be pointed. You could try downloading Hullcam VDS. It adds a 1st person EVA option:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/42739-11hullcam-vds-mod-up-for-adoption/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The_Rocketeer","CreatedById":81727,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T17:26:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709613\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470673509\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022147547\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dafidge9898\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, dafidge9898 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can\u0027t really fly from the kerbal\u0027s point of view if he\u0027s outside the spacecraft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/147547-dafidge9898/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022147547\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/147547-dafidge9898/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@dafidge9898\u003C/a\u003E, that pretty much sums up my point. \u003Cs\u003EBut as I understand it a Kerbal sitting in a command seat is considered to be \u0027inside\u0027 the spacecraft anyway, i.e. not on EVA - mass counts, resources are/become the ship\u0027s not the EVA packs, etc.\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-08T20:09:21Z\u0022 title=\u002208/08/2016 08:09  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 8, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by The_Rocketeer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T19:47:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709694\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470677188\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281727\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Rocketeer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The_Rocketeer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0resources are/become the ship\u0027s not the EVA packs, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat part is incorrect. An external command seat does not refill/share the EVA suit jetpack.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The_Rocketeer","CreatedById":81727,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T19:54:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709841\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470685668\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat part is incorrect. An external command seat does not refill/share the EVA suit jetpack.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nU sure about that? Does with TACLS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T20:06:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709846\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470686044\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281727\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Rocketeer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, The_Rocketeer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nU sure about that? Does with TACLS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust tested it in stock and verified.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The_Rocketeer","CreatedById":81727,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T20:08:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709859\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470686808\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust tested it in stock and verified.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFair enough, good call. Even so, I still don\u0027t see why it should be so hard to get an in-seat cam. Any suggestions on that line?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T20:21:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709861\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470686929\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281727\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Rocketeer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, The_Rocketeer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFair enough, good call. Even so, I still don\u0027t see why it should be so hard to get an in-seat cam. Any suggestions on that line?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how to do it myself, but I know that there is a way to manually choose the camera orientation. If you can give me a few hours, I think I can get some info from an expert.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-08T20:52:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222709861\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145603\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470686929\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002281727\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Rocketeer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The_Rocketeer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmmm. Sort of bad news so far. Stock seems to be mostly locked to the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECoM\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E of your vessel, with some limited horizontal and vertical movement.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, have you looked at this mod? It says it is 1.1.3 compatible now:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/122491-11-camera-focus-changer-v090\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: this camera mod seems more capable, but probably harder to use:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/84938-105-camera-tools-v151-dogfight-mode-autozoom-margin-slider-march-28/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;embedComment=2694181\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-08T22:19:36Z\u0022 title=\u002208/08/2016 10:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 8, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by bewing\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}